  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bc1, \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd, \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3 \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 - \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bc7\u0b9f \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Measures to resolve issues related to supply of gas, fuel, essential commodities - Presidential Special Report",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has said that steps have been taken to resolve the issues related to the supply of gas, fuel and essential goods.",
        "The President, who issued a special statement regarding the said issues this evening, said that the gas and fuel reserves will reach Sri Lanka by Tuesday, July 12.",
        "The President has requested the public not to be fooled by the false news spread by the opposition parties.",
        "Discussions with the International Monetary Fund (IMF) have been successful and the financing plan is expected to be launched within the next few weeks.",
        "\"After a long and well-planned effort, the country is reaping the benefits,\" he added.",
        "The first batch of 44,000 metric tonnes of fertilizer from India is due to arrive tomorrow.",
        "Continued supply of fuel, gas and essential commodities from July 12.",
        "The President informed that such measures have been taken and further informed that the Cabinet has approved the draft of the 22nd Amendment Act of the Constitution."
      ],
